<volume>OnReadyStateChange (JHTTPRequestEvents)</volume>
<interface>JHTTPRequestEvents</interface><method> OnReadyStateChange </method>
    <description>
        <para>
            HTTP 请求状态改变时触发。
        </para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> ECode </return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> ReadState  </param_type>
                <param_name> emuReadState </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
HTTP 请求的当前状态</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>
<remarks>
    <para>
        当 readState 为 <link url="../datatype/ReadState.htm">ReadState_INTERACTIVE</link> 时，该事件可能会被触发多次。更多回调事件信息，参见 Callback 机制介绍。
    </para>
</remarks>
